<db:para>This tutorial shows how items in a <db:link xlink:href="qml-qtquick-listview.xml">ListView</db:link> can be re-ordered without modifying the source model. It demonstrates using drag and drop to reposition individual items within a view and using model data to dynamically sort all items in a view.</db:para>
